sexpression.parser

Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • sexpression.parser.Parser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IParser

    public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
implements IParser
    This is a concrete parser implementation. It recognizes the strings #any, #string, #list as being special, wildcard strings. #list must be followed by a colon and then an sexp which defines the body of the list wildcard.
